07/27/17 -- CRH PLC (CRH). Press Release  Board change. 27 July 2017. CRH PLC (CRH), the international building materials group, announces that Maeve Carton, Group Transformation Director, has informed the directors of her intention to retire from the Board and from CRH on 31 August 2017.
















